

@*
This code appears to be a Razor view that renders a form for resetting a user's password.

Here's a summary of the steps:

Display the "Reset Password" header.
Create a row and a column using the Bootstrap grid system.
Inside the column, create a form that will submit to the "PostResetPassword" action when submitted.
Display any validation errors using the asp-validation-summary tag helper.
Create a form group for the SecurityQuestion property, displaying the label and input field with the SecurityQuestion property set as readonly.
Create a form group for the SecurityAnswer property, displaying the label and input field for the user to enter their security answer, with any validation errors displayed.
Create a form group for the NewPassword property, displaying the label and input field for the user to enter their new password, with any validation errors displayed.
Create a form group for the ConfirmPassword property, displaying the label and input field for the user to confirm their new password, with any validation errors displayed.
Display a submit button to reset the password.
